1)Create EC2 instance with Amzon linux AMI.
2)Add HTTP port in sercurity group so you can access your website.
3)Connect EC2 instance.
4)Install httpd server to host website.
  --sudo yum install httpd
5)Start httpd service using following commands.
  --systemctl start httpd
  --systemctl enabled httpd
6)Add your index.html and other files on following paths
  cd /var/www/html
7)Again restart the httpd service using bellow command.
  --systemctl restart httpd
8)Now you can access your website using server Public Ip
  ex)http://13.203.201.38/
